#!/usr/bin/env testml


*jsc.validate(*json) == *valid


=== Test 1 - validation of URI References - a valid URI
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"format": "uri-reference"}
--- json
"http://foo.bar/?baz=qux#quux"


=== Test 2 - validation of URI References - a valid protocol-relative URI Reference
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"//foo.bar/?baz=qux#quux"


=== Test 3 - validation of URI References - a valid relative URI Reference
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"/abc"


=== Test 4 - validation of URI References - an invalid URI Reference
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"\\\\WINDOWS\\fileshare"


=== Test 5 - validation of URI References - a valid URI Reference
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"abc"


=== Test 6 - validation of URI References - a valid URI fragment
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"#fragment"


=== Test 7 - validation of URI References - an invalid URI fragment
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"#frag\\ment"


